. Dust with icing sugar before cutting in squares and serving."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Cookidoo is full of inspiring cake recipes. Here, all of the preparation is done in your Thermomix, from chopping the chocolate to making orange-flavoured sugar and mixing the batter together. A great option when feeding a crowd, the pop of colour and flavour from the blueberries is simply delicious.","If using chocolate callets, omit <b>step 2<b> and add to mixture in <b>step 6.<b>"],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h","20 pieces"]}